      <title>Docs: Disk Optimization</title>
      <link>/docs/disk/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/disk/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        

&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Describes disk information and details provided by optimization strategy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;view-disk-information&#34;&gt;View disk information&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#view-disk-information&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click the &lt;code&gt;Disks&lt;/code&gt; menu on the left menu bar to display the disk page, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/disk/disk1_hu586b962710831052bb190f8f2f84d234_70715_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;291&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Disk
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Disk page are divided into tree areas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cluster selection area&lt;/strong&gt;: Used for select a cluster.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Query area&lt;/strong&gt;: Used for filtering disk by disk ID, instance ID and node name.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;List area&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays disk information, such as instances, usages and actions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After select a cluster, the list area will display node of the selected cluster scaned by &lt;strong&gt;Cluster Optimizer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;s optimization strategy, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/disk/disk2_huc4f6d93e34b39afdead8fc69986df97a_186869_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;443&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Disk: cluster selected
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The list area is divided into five columns:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Disk&lt;/strong&gt;: displays disk ID, device name, storage size and creation time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Owner&lt;/strong&gt;: displays information about resource&amp;rsquo;s owner, such as department, group and user.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instance&lt;/strong&gt;: displays the node ID, node name and region associate with the instance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Usage&lt;/strong&gt;: displays disk capacity, maximum utilization, average utilization and last update time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Action&lt;/strong&gt;: displays actions on the disk.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;adjust-disk&#34;&gt;Adjust disk&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#adjust-disk&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;code&gt;Adjust&lt;/code&gt; link to in action colum above, it will open the &lt;code&gt;Adjust Disk Size&lt;/code&gt; dialog, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/disk/disk3_huc497cd330fcd67249832763c798ad846_88237_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;387&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Disk: adjust disk size
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;


      </description>
